{"tid":221041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天舟一號成功為天宮二號進行「太空加油」","createTime":"2017-04-28T11:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T14:27:45.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"412edffa253c24153c2b63a14df2957d00d7e131","tid":221041,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"天舟一號與天宮二號今晚7時7分成功完成首次推進劑在軌補加試驗，標誌天舟一號飛行任務取得圓滿成功。按計劃，天舟一號將在6月中下旬進行第二次推進劑在軌補加試驗，進一步鞏固取得的技術成果。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，在中國成功突破和掌握推進劑在軌補加關鍵技術前，僅有俄羅斯與美國掌握此項技術。"},{"pid":"a4e0aa39f560e139ff4bae71fe0ca8d99634cc33","tid":221041,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:59:17.000Z","msg":"如果拎高鐵啲錢做科研，香港係唔係可以整到gundam"},{"pid":"f5d0ceb1f48fbe0e174a281b04caa21a1c8b7670","tid":221041,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果拎高鐵啲錢做科研，香港係唔係可以整到gundam</blockquote><br />\nno<br />\n<br />\n香港技術沙漠"},{"pid":"53b8882768262fef0432dcf6cb1320a539ddd993","tid":221041,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果拎高鐵啲錢做科研，香港係唔係可以整到gundam</blockquote><br />\nno<br />\n<br />\n香港技術沙漠</blockquote><br />\n尊者高達呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef786dbc31c31f4b5672e8d64f7259091678f968","tid":221041,"uid":4031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"924497456adf562d3b8a963e734bd142f1feaa16","tid":221041,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}